{"tid":1067252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比起平板6.4我覺得...","createTime":"2019-03-18T11:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T13:02:04.000Z","uid":162499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7153b84237acc56fc5b59707124d0f7a869ed304","tid":1067252,"uid":162499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"都已經過左20就30年,到依定為止都仲係革命尚未成功,同志仍需努力既階段...究竟和理非非真係做到幾多野我真係唔知,但成30年連隻蛋都生唔出真係好冇用囉...感覺佢地仲沉醉係當年百萬人上街之後令老_董腳痛既回憶,真係好難怪8,90後對佢地失望...<br />\n<br />\n1989年我未出世,所以我了解當年既事並唔多,但依家過左咁耐,關於6.4既歷史教科書1本都冇...都應該差唔多要放棄所謂建設民主中国呢D咁天真咁傻既諗法...<br />\n<br />\n事到如今,香港人要自救仲平反6.4真係曬9氣,平反雨傘,魚蛋仲可能有用過佢"},{"pid":"7e6c0dc2231c9084aed0e8391c53d08ac403962d","tid":1067252,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:44:43.000Z","msg":"而家一講就觸動中共神經<br />\n<br />\n係台灣立國、香港獨立、西藏獨立"},{"pid":"a9c5e7921232ac2d0f714e690629bec352458e6d","tid":1067252,"uid":162499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7e6c0dc2231c9084aed0e8391c53d08ac403962d","tid":1067252,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:44:43.000Z","msg":"而家一講就觸動中共神經<br />\n<br />\n係台灣立國、香港獨立、西藏獨立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:40:15.000Z","msg":"咁有咩係唔會觸動中共神經既先?全身都係G點"},{"pid":"5b9caef1bf8e83a003143600a39d92e9564513f8","tid":1067252,"uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20110308/large/08lp2p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20110308%2Flarge%2F08lp2p8.jpg&h=7d468278&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3602bcbe5df4b221b39b8cc250f67d0707e2f0f8","tid":1067252,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:53:39.000Z","msg":"咁多年嚟證明咗泛民借六四搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6cc68218139a10b05f02ed087ec5bd56bb6e5d","tid":1067